# üìù NOTES
# =====================================================
#
# Why sync: false in render.yaml?
# - Security: Secrets should not be in version control
# - Flexibility: Different values per environment
# - Compliance: Follow security best practices
#
# Why does API crash without OPENAI_API_KEY?
# - Scheduler starts on API startup (main.py:3050)
# - AI News Bulletin job runs every 15 minutes
# - Job requires OpenAI client to generate summaries
# - Without key ‚Üí OpenAI client fails ‚Üí API crashes
#
# Can I disable OpenAI temporarily?
# - Not recommended (breaks core features)
# - Better: Get a free OpenAI key ($5 credit)
# - Alternative: Comment out scheduler in main.py
